<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Read Faster — Support</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family:
          -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica,
          Arial, sans-serif;
        max-width: 680px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 40px 20px;
        color: #1d1d1f;
        line-height: 1.6;
        background: #fff;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 28px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }
      h2 {
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-top: 32px;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }
      p {
        margin: 8px 0;
      }
      ul {
        margin: 8px 0;
        padding-left: 24px;
      }
      li {
        margin: 4px 0;
      }
      a {
        color: #0066cc;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Read Faster — Support</h1>

    <h2>Getting Started</h2>
    <p>
      Import books (EPUB, PDF, or TXT) by tapping the <strong>+</strong> button in
      the Library tab, or by opening a file from the Files app. Tap a book to start
      reading.
    </p>

    <h2>Reading Controls</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Tap the word display to play/pause</li>
      <li>Swipe left/right to skip sentences</li>
      <li>Use the scrub bar to jump to any position</li>
      <li>
        Adjust speed with the WPM control (−/+ or tap to expand the slider)
      </li>
      <li>Toggle between 1-word and 3-word modes at the bottom</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Chapters</h2>
    <p>
      For EPUBs and PDFs with chapter data, tap the chapter button next to the
      title to navigate between chapters.
    </p>

    <h2>Requirements</h2>
    <p>iOS 26.0 or later. iPhone and iPad.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      For bug reports or feature requests, email
      <a href="mailto:jjalangtry@gmail.com">jjalangtry@gmail.com</a>.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
